{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/others/productivity-presentation/productivity-presentation/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yajana Rao"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a0ecc600-fe9c-5595-b34a-b0c55e6ae52c","excerpt":"productivity = amount of work done / working hours Create/reorganize a home office or dedicated workspace, a space you love. … Set boundaries for people in your…","html":"<p>productivity = amount of work done / working hours</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Create/reorganize a home office or dedicated workspace, a space you love. …</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Set boundaries for people in your home (door sign)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>morning routine</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Writing down your goals for the day.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Prioritize your work, Do the hardest things first. (Todoist)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 531px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/036cdd923e9be928a4c4890cb4764197/d4713/Untitled.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled.png\"\n        src=\"/static/036cdd923e9be928a4c4890cb4764197/d4713/Untitled.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/036cdd923e9be928a4c4890cb4764197/12f09/Untitled.png 148w,\n/static/036cdd923e9be928a4c4890cb4764197/e4a3f/Untitled.png 295w,\n/static/036cdd923e9be928a4c4890cb4764197/d4713/Untitled.png 531w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 531px) 100vw, 531px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Make it harder for yourself to mess around on social media.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Silence notifications</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Socialize directly with people instead.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>No screen time until breakfast.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Improve your mental well-being</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Take strategic breaks.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Learn to say no</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Pick a definitive stop time each day -> be more productive</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Listen to relaxing sounds → my case, beach sounds</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go outside</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Have virtual water cooler chats\nA 2018 survey showed that 20% of remote workers feel that loneliness is their biggest struggle with working remotely</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>what is focus?</p>\n<p>essentially when you lose yourself into what you’re doing, lose track of time, you’re on auto-pilot</p>\n<p>2m trick</p>\n<p>pomodoro</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>productivity vs organization</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7bf7c82ae1bfd80cad0378a9c7e9b714/e24fe/second.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/second.png\"\n        title=\"/second.png\"\n        src=\"/static/7bf7c82ae1bfd80cad0378a9c7e9b714/fcda8/second.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7bf7c82ae1bfd80cad0378a9c7e9b714/12f09/second.png 148w,\n/static/7bf7c82ae1bfd80cad0378a9c7e9b714/e4a3f/second.png 295w,\n/static/7bf7c82ae1bfd80cad0378a9c7e9b714/fcda8/second.png 590w,\n/static/7bf7c82ae1bfd80cad0378a9c7e9b714/efc66/second.png 885w,\n/static/7bf7c82ae1bfd80cad0378a9c7e9b714/e24fe/second.png 1073w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>when can you focus?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e592d845c184cb7c5c649105625a13b/142fb/Untitled2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled2.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled2.png\"\n        src=\"/static/1e592d845c184cb7c5c649105625a13b/fcda8/Untitled2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e592d845c184cb7c5c649105625a13b/12f09/Untitled2.png 148w,\n/static/1e592d845c184cb7c5c649105625a13b/e4a3f/Untitled2.png 295w,\n/static/1e592d845c184cb7c5c649105625a13b/fcda8/Untitled2.png 590w,\n/static/1e592d845c184cb7c5c649105625a13b/efc66/Untitled2.png 885w,\n/static/1e592d845c184cb7c5c649105625a13b/142fb/Untitled2.png 907w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>physical world vs remote / home world</p>\n<p>chronotypes</p>\n<p>life organization</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>3 biggest mistakes</p>\n<ul>\n<li>saying yes</li>\n<li>being reactive</li>\n<li>over planning</li>\n</ul>\n<p>SET DEEP FOCUS TIME</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Reflection!</h2>\n<p>How do you prioritize your work?</p>\n<p>From what we’ve spoken, what was 1 thing that stood out in your eyes?</p>\n<p>How can you implement this one?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>what influences our focus?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7251509f11dc6010692a8c7ae83ee1f1/aa61c/Untitled3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.27027027027027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled3.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled3.png\"\n        src=\"/static/7251509f11dc6010692a8c7ae83ee1f1/fcda8/Untitled3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7251509f11dc6010692a8c7ae83ee1f1/12f09/Untitled3.png 148w,\n/static/7251509f11dc6010692a8c7ae83ee1f1/e4a3f/Untitled3.png 295w,\n/static/7251509f11dc6010692a8c7ae83ee1f1/fcda8/Untitled3.png 590w,\n/static/7251509f11dc6010692a8c7ae83ee1f1/efc66/Untitled3.png 885w,\n/static/7251509f11dc6010692a8c7ae83ee1f1/aa61c/Untitled3.png 1065w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Dopamine!!!</p>\n<p>our brain is wired for: instant gratification, quick fix, path of least resistance</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>how to get dopamine levels to a balanced level?</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Eat Lots of Protein</li>\n<li>Eat Less Saturated Fat</li>\n<li>Consume Probiotics</li>\n<li>Eat Velvet Beans.</li>\n<li>Exercise Often</li>\n<li>Get Enough Sleep</li>\n<li>Listen to Music</li>\n<li>Meditate</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>how to deal with distractions:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/430ddedd00b954f2b7938fde294d5bf3/dd104/Untitled4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.94594594594595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled4.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled4.png\"\n        src=\"/static/430ddedd00b954f2b7938fde294d5bf3/fcda8/Untitled4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/430ddedd00b954f2b7938fde294d5bf3/12f09/Untitled4.png 148w,\n/static/430ddedd00b954f2b7938fde294d5bf3/e4a3f/Untitled4.png 295w,\n/static/430ddedd00b954f2b7938fde294d5bf3/fcda8/Untitled4.png 590w,\n/static/430ddedd00b954f2b7938fde294d5bf3/efc66/Untitled4.png 885w,\n/static/430ddedd00b954f2b7938fde294d5bf3/dd104/Untitled4.png 1064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Reflection!</h2>\n<p>What is your biggest distraction?</p>\n<p>How can you tackle it?</p>\n<p>How and when are you going to do that? (make a time slot in your calendar now)</p>\n<h1>Energy</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3396056626ea435103d76747406a480d/6db71/Untitled5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled5.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled5.png\"\n        src=\"/static/3396056626ea435103d76747406a480d/fcda8/Untitled5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3396056626ea435103d76747406a480d/12f09/Untitled5.png 148w,\n/static/3396056626ea435103d76747406a480d/e4a3f/Untitled5.png 295w,\n/static/3396056626ea435103d76747406a480d/fcda8/Untitled5.png 590w,\n/static/3396056626ea435103d76747406a480d/6db71/Untitled5.png 659w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>physical, brain, heart (emotions), spirituality (mind, mindfulness)</p>\n<h2>Physical</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>nutrition</li>\n<li>sleep</li>\n<li>exercise</li>\n<li>stress management</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/23272b0e9236c9dcc20015da2a9c89d8/4e6ec/Untitled6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.27027027027026%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled6.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled6.png\"\n        src=\"/static/23272b0e9236c9dcc20015da2a9c89d8/fcda8/Untitled6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/23272b0e9236c9dcc20015da2a9c89d8/12f09/Untitled6.png 148w,\n/static/23272b0e9236c9dcc20015da2a9c89d8/e4a3f/Untitled6.png 295w,\n/static/23272b0e9236c9dcc20015da2a9c89d8/fcda8/Untitled6.png 590w,\n/static/23272b0e9236c9dcc20015da2a9c89d8/4e6ec/Untitled6.png 827w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/70353a77c37bd00425dfc657002e35d4/587b0/Untitled7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled7.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled7.png\"\n        src=\"/static/70353a77c37bd00425dfc657002e35d4/fcda8/Untitled7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/70353a77c37bd00425dfc657002e35d4/12f09/Untitled7.png 148w,\n/static/70353a77c37bd00425dfc657002e35d4/e4a3f/Untitled7.png 295w,\n/static/70353a77c37bd00425dfc657002e35d4/fcda8/Untitled7.png 590w,\n/static/70353a77c37bd00425dfc657002e35d4/efc66/Untitled7.png 885w,\n/static/70353a77c37bd00425dfc657002e35d4/587b0/Untitled7.png 970w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d5990d8ac3ef3cbe37a3800a7ab13154/ad12c/Untitled8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled8.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled8.png\"\n        src=\"/static/d5990d8ac3ef3cbe37a3800a7ab13154/fcda8/Untitled8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d5990d8ac3ef3cbe37a3800a7ab13154/12f09/Untitled8.png 148w,\n/static/d5990d8ac3ef3cbe37a3800a7ab13154/e4a3f/Untitled8.png 295w,\n/static/d5990d8ac3ef3cbe37a3800a7ab13154/fcda8/Untitled8.png 590w,\n/static/d5990d8ac3ef3cbe37a3800a7ab13154/ad12c/Untitled8.png 856w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Emotions</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/465eb73fcbe634de49606b5156ba2054/0fcea/Untitled9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.48648648648649%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled9.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled9.png\"\n        src=\"/static/465eb73fcbe634de49606b5156ba2054/fcda8/Untitled9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/465eb73fcbe634de49606b5156ba2054/12f09/Untitled9.png 148w,\n/static/465eb73fcbe634de49606b5156ba2054/e4a3f/Untitled9.png 295w,\n/static/465eb73fcbe634de49606b5156ba2054/fcda8/Untitled9.png 590w,\n/static/465eb73fcbe634de49606b5156ba2054/0fcea/Untitled9.png 851w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Reflection:</h3>\n<p>What situations trigger your negative emotions?</p>\n<p>What are you fighting for?</p>\n<p>What are you fleeing from?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0b652698f2b427575a925d360164e1e8/5a190/Untitled10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.78378378378378%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled10.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled10.png\"\n        src=\"/static/0b652698f2b427575a925d360164e1e8/fcda8/Untitled10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0b652698f2b427575a925d360164e1e8/12f09/Untitled10.png 148w,\n/static/0b652698f2b427575a925d360164e1e8/e4a3f/Untitled10.png 295w,\n/static/0b652698f2b427575a925d360164e1e8/fcda8/Untitled10.png 590w,\n/static/0b652698f2b427575a925d360164e1e8/5a190/Untitled10.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>creating an habit:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>make it visible (can’t forget it)</li>\n<li>make it attractive (appealing to achieve, what are the benefits?) dopamine, anticipation</li>\n<li>make it easy (2m rule)</li>\n<li>make it satisfying (have a partner do it with you) habit tracking, paper clip strat</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 358px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b03a904fdff70be719328d383d9563b8/39185/Untitled11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.621621621621614%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"/Untitled11.png\"\n        title=\"/Untitled11.png\"\n        src=\"/static/b03a904fdff70be719328d383d9563b8/39185/Untitled11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b03a904fdff70be719328d383d9563b8/12f09/Untitled11.png 148w,\n/static/b03a904fdff70be719328d383d9563b8/e4a3f/Untitled11.png 295w,\n/static/b03a904fdff70be719328d383d9563b8/39185/Untitled11.png 358w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 358px) 100vw, 358px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:midd